metadata.name: Seeds of Contemplation - Eikyouryoku na Niwa 1
metadata.description: 'Seeds of Contemplation' features a pensive individual with a hand over their eye and head, symbolizing the introspective journey we all undertake as we navigate the garden of life. The subject grapples with the weight of their decisions and the quest for meaning.'Eikyouryoku na Niwa: Reflections and Regrets' is a captivating collection that explores the profound impact of our choices, both on ourselves and the world around us.
